# Component placement

**`src/lib`** — Svelte surface UI. **`src/ui`** — canvas/editor TS (no Svelte).

- Feature = one folder. Node stacks use `node/` + `node/parameters/`. Shared primitives → `lib/components/ui/{button,menu,input,icon,overlay,display,...}`.
- Major chrome: **`top-bar/`**, **`bottom-bar/`**, **`side-panel/`**, editor split **`lib/components/editor/`** + **`ui/editor/{canvas,rendering}/`**.
- Folders **kebab-case** when multiword (`side-panel`); otherwise single noun (`timeline`, `audio`).
- Exported “main” per feature (`TopBar`, …); internals named **`MainRole`** (`TopBarViewControls`). Barrel exports surface only the façade unless a slot demands more.
- New work lands in owning feature dirs; primitives only in **`lib/components/ui/`**; node-only controls → **`node/parameters/`**.
- **`lib`** imports **`ui/editor`** (optional **`ui/interactions`**) strictly via **`index.ts`** — no deep `ui/` paths.

Diagram + migration notes: **`docs/architecture/component-structure-consultation.md`**.
